harder to get than that.

260
00:15:05,113 --> 00:15:07,114
-Oh, okay. Really?
-Uh-huh.

261
00:15:07,115 --> 00:15:09,158
But I could teach
you some Mandarin.

262
00:15:09,159 --> 00:15:13,370
