01:05:30,510 --> 01:05:32,345
<i>That is one point.
Buddha Stevens.</i>

1018
01:05:32,346 --> 01:05:33,804
Welcome to the 5 Boroughs.

1019
01:05:33,805 --> 01:05:35,264
<i>Let's see if Fong can recover.</i>

