1024
01:05:50,697 --> 01:05:51,990
<i>Tough luck, Buddha!</i>

1025
01:05:57,496 --> 01:06:00,247
<i>Yama-zuki</i>. Punching
block. Stronger base.

1026
01:06:00,248 --> 01:06:03,334
Windmill block more dynamic.

